---
// Vertical workflow diagram with branching — same structure as the styleguide.
// Self-contained: drops in anywhere on the page, sits on a dot-grid backdrop.
---

<section class="section" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container stack-6">
    <span class="eyebrow"
      >How it works</span
    >
    <h2>One workflow. <span class="italic-accent">Built for you.</span></h2>
    <p>
      Every system we build follows the same skeleton. Lead in, score, route,
      convert. The active path carries crimson. Status pills float beside live
      nodes.
    </p>

    <div class="dot-grid" style="margin-top:24px">
      <div class="flow-v">
        <div class="flow-node active">
          <div class="flow-node-head">
            <div class="flow-node-icon">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle><path
                  d="M3 12h6M15 12h6M12 3v6M12 15v6"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <div class="flow-node-title">When new lead found</div>
            <span class="type-pill">Leads</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-node-body">
            Triggers when a person is added to the Q2 outbound list and matches
            the ICP filters.
          </div>
          <span class="status-pill flow">Triggered</span>
        </div>

        <div class="v-conn live">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 320 56" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <line class="line" x1="160" y1="0" x2="160" y2="48"></line>
            <polygon class="arrow" points="155,48 160,56 165,48"></polygon>
            <circle class="dot" cx="160" cy="0" r="3"></circle>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-node active">
          <div class="flow-node-head">
            <div class="flow-node-icon">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path
                  d="M3 6h13M16 6l3 3-3 3M21 18H8M8 18l-3-3 3-3"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <div class="flow-node-title">Score & route</div>
            <span class="type-pill">Condition</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-node-body">
            Routes to a sequence based on ICP score, intent signal, and
            territory.
          </div>
          <span class="status-pill positive">Completed</span>
        </div>

        <div class="branch-fan">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 680 80" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path
              class="line"
              d="M340,0 V36"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              class="line"
              d="M340,36 H170 V72"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <polygon class="arrow" points="165,72 170,80 175,72"></polygon>
            <path
              class="line muted"
              d="M340,36 H510 V72"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <polygon class="arrow muted" points="505,72 510,80 515,72"
            ></polygon>
          </svg>
          <span class="branch-label" style="left:25%; top:48%"
            >Hot · score ≥ 80</span
          >
          <span class="branch-label muted" style="left:75%; top:48%"
            >Cold · score &lt; 80</span
          >
        </div>

        <div class="branch-row">
          <div class="flow-node active">
            <div class="flow-node-head">
              <div class="flow-node-icon">
                <svg
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="m22 2-7 20-4-9-9-4Z"></path><path d="M22 2 11 13"
                  ></path></svg
                >
              </div>
              <div class="flow-node-title">Add to Q2 sequence</div>
              <span class="type-pill">Sequences</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flow-node-body">
              Enrolls the person in the high-intent Q2 outbound sequence with
              day-1 send.
            </div>
            <span class="status-pill positive">Completed</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-node">
            <div class="flow-node-head">
              <div class="flow-node-icon">
                <svg
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path
                    d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path></svg
                >
              </div>
              <div class="flow-node-title">Park in nurture</div>
              <span class="type-pill">Sequences</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flow-node-body">
              Re-evaluates in 90 days when score crosses the threshold or a new
              signal fires.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="flow-add" aria-label="Add step">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            ><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"></path></svg
          >
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
